    "id": "grok-builder-prompts-troptions-unity",
    "filename": "grok-builder-prompts-troptions-unity.md",
    "title": "Ready-to-Paste Grok Builder Prompts — Troptions Unity Legacy Vault (Updated Pricing + PLONK/Poseidon)",
